WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.438 --> 00:00:07.874
Narrator: IT TOOK JUST 18 HOURS
FOR POMPEII

00:00:07.874 --> 00:00:09.376
TO BE BURIED UNDER MILLIONS

00:00:09.376 --> 00:00:12.178
OF TONS OF VOLCANIC
ASH AND PUMICE.

00:00:14.314 --> 00:00:17.050
AN ENTIRE LIVING CITY
WIPED OUT,

00:00:17.050 --> 00:00:22.321
THOUSANDS OF ITS PEOPLE
BURIED ALIVE.

00:00:22.321 --> 00:00:24.724
THE SUPER-HEATED AIR
BURNS THEIR LUNGS

00:00:24.724 --> 00:00:26.625
AND MELTS THEIR MUSCLES.

00:00:26.625 --> 00:00:28.595
THEIR TWISTED
AND CONTORTED BODIES

00:00:28.595 --> 00:00:30.897
WERE QUICKLY BURIED IN ASH.

00:00:32.698 --> 00:00:36.735
A TEAM OF SCIENTISTS IS NOW
STUDYING 15 BODIES

00:00:36.735 --> 00:00:39.405
THAT WERE FOUND TOGETHER
IN THE EAST OF THE CITY.

00:00:39.405 --> 00:00:42.108
THE ODD POSITIONS
THESE BODIES WERE FOUND

00:00:42.108 --> 00:00:45.779
IN INTRIGUES TEAM
LEADER LLORENç ALAPONT.

00:01:03.629 --> 00:01:06.198
Narrator: TO DO SO,
THEY'RE SCANNING THE CASTS

00:01:06.198 --> 00:01:08.734
IN MORE DETAIL
THAN EVER BEFORE,

00:01:08.734 --> 00:01:11.036
TAKING HIGH-RESOLUTION
PHOTOGRAPHS

00:01:11.036 --> 00:01:14.474
AND THEN X-RAYS
OF THEIR BONES LOCKED INSIDE.

00:01:30.423 --> 00:01:34.494
Narrator: ONE CAST IS
PARTICULARLY WELL PRESERVED.

00:01:34.494 --> 00:01:37.263
LLORENç HAS ALREADY
UNLOCKED PERSONAL DETAILS

00:01:37.263 --> 00:01:39.632
OF THIS MAN'S LIFE.

00:01:44.770 --> 00:01:47.506
THIS YOUNG MAN ALSO HAD
A MILITARY SWORD,

00:01:47.506 --> 00:01:50.143
WHICH LEADS LLORENç
TO THINK HE WAS A SOLDIER.

00:02:04.457 --> 00:02:07.327
Narrator: THE WELL-PRESERVED
SECTIONS OF THE CAST ARE COPIED

00:02:07.327 --> 00:02:09.495
AND THEN FILLED
INTO OTHER SECTIONS

00:02:09.495 --> 00:02:11.197
THAT ARE LESS DETAILED.

00:02:22.041 --> 00:02:24.343
Narrator: THE RESULT IS AN IMAGE
THAT IS MOVING

00:02:24.343 --> 00:02:27.212
AND STRIKINGLY LIFELIKE
OF THE YOUNG SOLDIER

00:02:27.212 --> 00:02:29.649
WHO WAS BURIED 2,000 YEARS AGO.

